9 CHAPTER 51. AUTHORITY FOR MUNICIPALITIES TO IMPLEMENT RENT
10 STABILIZATION
11 §9731. Authority for municipalities to implement rent stabilization
12 A municipality or parish may, by a majority vote of its governing authority,
13 adopt ordinances to implement rent stabilization measures.
